{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-changelog-js","path":"/changelog/2019/january","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"getting-started\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#getting-started\" aria-label=\"getting started permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Getting Started</h3>\n<p>We introduce the new <a href=\"/hackers/hacker-dashboard.html\">Getting Started</a> page on the Hacker Dashboard. This will guide hackers and direct them to the right pages to help them get the information they need to successfully start out on HackerOne</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"getting started\"\n        title=\"getting started\"\n        src=\"/static/3636cede8c5526e434c109712c349d05/0b533/jan_2019_getting_started.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3636cede8c5526e434c109712c349d05/fac75/jan_2019_getting_started.png 125w,\n/static/3636cede8c5526e434c109712c349d05/63868/jan_2019_getting_started.png 250w,\n/static/3636cede8c5526e434c109712c349d05/0b533/jan_2019_getting_started.png 500w,\n/static/3636cede8c5526e434c109712c349d05/1d69c/jan_2019_getting_started.png 750w,\n/static/3636cede8c5526e434c109712c349d05/00d43/jan_2019_getting_started.png 1000w,\n/static/3636cede8c5526e434c109712c349d05/2c960/jan_2019_getting_started.png 2870w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"export-all-reports\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#export-all-reports\" aria-label=\"export all reports permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Export All Reports</h3>\n<p>Want all of your report data for safe keeping or just for analytical purposes? Programs can now export all of their reports through our new <a href=\"/programs/export-reports.html\">Export Reports</a> feature.  </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"export reports\"\n        title=\"export reports\"\n        src=\"/static/853fecf303134ed3dd0de4bee5b97afe/0b533/jan_2019_export_reports.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/853fecf303134ed3dd0de4bee5b97afe/fac75/jan_2019_export_reports.png 125w,\n/static/853fecf303134ed3dd0de4bee5b97afe/63868/jan_2019_export_reports.png 250w,\n/static/853fecf303134ed3dd0de4bee5b97afe/0b533/jan_2019_export_reports.png 500w,\n/static/853fecf303134ed3dd0de4bee5b97afe/1d69c/jan_2019_export_reports.png 750w,\n/static/853fecf303134ed3dd0de4bee5b97afe/00d43/jan_2019_export_reports.png 1000w,\n/static/853fecf303134ed3dd0de4bee5b97afe/d4377/jan_2019_export_reports.png 1294w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"link-hackerone-reports-to-existing-jira-tasks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#link-hackerone-reports-to-existing-jira-tasks\" aria-label=\"link hackerone reports to existing jira tasks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Link HackerOne Reports to Existing Jira Tasks</h3>\n<p>Jira users can now <a href=\"/programs/jira-integration.html\">link</a> their HackerOne reports to their existing Jira tasks.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linking HackerOne to Jira\"\n        title=\"linking HackerOne to Jira\"\n        src=\"/static/1b2240720904e132ac0e9e6458893ce8/0b533/jan_2019_link_jira.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1b2240720904e132ac0e9e6458893ce8/fac75/jan_2019_link_jira.png 125w,\n/static/1b2240720904e132ac0e9e6458893ce8/63868/jan_2019_link_jira.png 250w,\n/static/1b2240720904e132ac0e9e6458893ce8/0b533/jan_2019_link_jira.png 500w,\n/static/1b2240720904e132ac0e9e6458893ce8/1d69c/jan_2019_link_jira.png 750w,\n/static/1b2240720904e132ac0e9e6458893ce8/00d43/jan_2019_link_jira.png 1000w,\n/static/1b2240720904e132ac0e9e6458893ce8/e67dd/jan_2019_link_jira.png 1801w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"selecting-from-multiple-jira-projects\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#selecting-from-multiple-jira-projects\" aria-label=\"selecting from multiple jira projects permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Selecting From Multiple Jira Projects</h3>\n<p>Jira users can also now select from multiple projects they want their Jira task to link to.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 330px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"selecting projects\"\n        title=\"selecting projects\"\n        src=\"/static/cb3ac210077b4a09d979695ecaa7a9b8/d9ecf/jan_2019_jira_projects.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cb3ac210077b4a09d979695ecaa7a9b8/fac75/jan_2019_jira_projects.png 125w,\n/static/cb3ac210077b4a09d979695ecaa7a9b8/63868/jan_2019_jira_projects.png 250w,\n/static/cb3ac210077b4a09d979695ecaa7a9b8/d9ecf/jan_2019_jira_projects.png 330w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 330px) 100vw, 330px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"indian-rupee-payments\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#indian-rupee-payments\" aria-label=\"indian rupee payments permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Indian Rupee Payments</h3>\n<p>Hackers in India will no longer lose a portion of their bounty to transfer fees as we now support payments to <a href=\"https://www.hackerone.com/blog/Introducing-Indian-Rupee-payments-Cheaper-and-faster-bank-transfers\">Indian Rupees</a>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 97.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"adding Indian Rupee\"\n        title=\"adding Indian Rupee\"\n        src=\"/static/57ac4cbb4db57e2be30f4d57dcd1df2c/0b533/jan_2019_indian_rupee.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/57ac4cbb4db57e2be30f4d57dcd1df2c/fac75/jan_2019_indian_rupee.png 125w,\n/static/57ac4cbb4db57e2be30f4d57dcd1df2c/63868/jan_2019_indian_rupee.png 250w,\n/static/57ac4cbb4db57e2be30f4d57dcd1df2c/0b533/jan_2019_indian_rupee.png 500w,\n/static/57ac4cbb4db57e2be30f4d57dcd1df2c/dea13/jan_2019_indian_rupee.png 514w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"improved-sign-up-page\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#improved-sign-up-page\" aria-label=\"improved sign up page permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Improved Sign Up Page</h3>\n<p>When new users sign up to use HackerOne, they can can now more clearly distinguish whether they are a hacker or a company wanting to set up an account.  </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sign up branching page\"\n        title=\"sign up branching page\"\n        src=\"/static/d2a8009782285aba0483792e52041d02/0b533/jan_2019_signup.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d2a8009782285aba0483792e52041d02/fac75/jan_2019_signup.png 125w,\n/static/d2a8009782285aba0483792e52041d02/63868/jan_2019_signup.png 250w,\n/static/d2a8009782285aba0483792e52041d02/0b533/jan_2019_signup.png 500w,\n/static/d2a8009782285aba0483792e52041d02/1d69c/jan_2019_signup.png 750w,\n/static/d2a8009782285aba0483792e52041d02/00d43/jan_2019_signup.png 1000w,\n/static/d2a8009782285aba0483792e52041d02/874d1/jan_2019_signup.png 1310w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"account-preferences\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#account-preferences\" aria-label=\"account preferences permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Account Preferences</h3>\n<p>You can now clearly define whether you're a hacker or someone running a program within the new Account Preferences tab under your profile settings. This will help tailor your HackerOne experience to better fit your needs.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"account preferences\"\n        title=\"account preferences\"\n        src=\"/static/7cf90f29e9bfb20d89937dc8ce3538c1/0b533/jan_2019_account_preferences.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7cf90f29e9bfb20d89937dc8ce3538c1/fac75/jan_2019_account_preferences.png 125w,\n/static/7cf90f29e9bfb20d89937dc8ce3538c1/63868/jan_2019_account_preferences.png 250w,\n/static/7cf90f29e9bfb20d89937dc8ce3538c1/0b533/jan_2019_account_preferences.png 500w,\n/static/7cf90f29e9bfb20d89937dc8ce3538c1/1d69c/jan_2019_account_preferences.png 750w,\n/static/7cf90f29e9bfb20d89937dc8ce3538c1/00d43/jan_2019_account_preferences.png 1000w,\n/static/7cf90f29e9bfb20d89937dc8ce3538c1/7ef4c/jan_2019_account_preferences.png 1748w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"infinite-scrolling\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#infinite-scrolling\" aria-label=\"infinite scrolling permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Infinite Scrolling</h3>\n<p>We've now implemented infinite scrolling on multiple pages so that you no longer have to click on the <i>Load more</i> button to view more information. The information now automatically populates.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"infinite scrolling\"\n        title=\"infinite scrolling\"\n        src=\"/static/1f9c1b653a2eb59b48cc0d1a0758a75f/0b533/jan_2019_infitine_scrolling.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1f9c1b653a2eb59b48cc0d1a0758a75f/fac75/jan_2019_infitine_scrolling.png 125w,\n/static/1f9c1b653a2eb59b48cc0d1a0758a75f/63868/jan_2019_infitine_scrolling.png 250w,\n/static/1f9c1b653a2eb59b48cc0d1a0758a75f/0b533/jan_2019_infitine_scrolling.png 500w,\n/static/1f9c1b653a2eb59b48cc0d1a0758a75f/1d69c/jan_2019_infitine_scrolling.png 750w,\n/static/1f9c1b653a2eb59b48cc0d1a0758a75f/00d43/jan_2019_infitine_scrolling.png 1000w,\n/static/1f9c1b653a2eb59b48cc0d1a0758a75f/b5a09/jan_2019_infitine_scrolling.png 1360w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/changelog/2019/january","title":"January 2019"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}